{{gherdëina}}[[File:Plan dai Ciavei Puez Gherdëina.jpg|thumb|350px|Ududa de Plan dai Ciavei.]]L '''Plan dai Ciavei''' ie na [[mont]] te [[Puez]] tl [[Parch naturel Puez-Odles]] tla [[Dolomites]]. La mont ie sëura [[Pra da Rì]] danter [[Piz Duleda]], [[Piz de Puez]] y [[Col dala Pieres]].

== Troies ==
Tres l Plan dai Ciavei porta l [[troi]] Nr. 2 che va dala [[utia de Puez]] ala [[furcela de Nives]] y la [[furcela de Forces de Sieles]]<ref>[https://www.openstreetmap.org/?mlat=46.534&mlon=11.703072&zoom=11#map=14/46.5864/11.7947 Cherta di troies de Puez sun Open street Map.]</ref>.

L Plan dai Ciavei ie dant al dut dinstà na pastura per biesces.
